<section class="three-playground" id="threePlayground">
  <canvas id="threePlaygroundCanvas" class="three-playground-canvas" aria-label="WebGL interactive cosmic ribbons"></canvas>
  <div class="three-playground-rings" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="three-playground-vignette"></div>

  <div class="three-playground-panel">
    <p class="three-playground-kicker">Interactive WebGL Lab</p>
    <h1>星河涟漪</h1>
    <p>
      点击会在不同位置叠加三组独立冲击波，连续点两次会形成交叉干涉；按住 Shift 点击会触发更强爆发。移动鼠标拖拽星河，滚轮推进视角。
    </p>
    <div class="three-playground-actions">
      <a href="/blog/" class="three-playground-btn">返回博客</a>
      <button class="three-playground-btn ghost" type="button" id="threePlaygroundShuffle">切换：星河</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="three-playground-hud" aria-hidden="true">
    <span>CLICK: 叠加涟漪</span>
    <span>SHIFT + CLICK: 强爆发</span>
    <span>WHEEL: 推拉视角</span>
  </div>
</section>
